<section class="your-adventure">
  <div class="container-fluid">
    <div class="col-lg-7 col-md-9">
      <div class="bracket-text">
        <h1 style="font-weight: 400;">SHARE YOUR CANADA</h1>
    		<h1>WIN A TRIP HOME</h1>
    		<h3>Explorers’ Edge wants to bring one lucky Canadian ex-pat and a guest home to celebrate Canada’s 150th birthday! To be eligible to win, simply upload your ‘great Canadian wilderness’ story and photo between April 13 and May 20, 2017. Then from May 22 to June 26, 2017, invite your friends in your new country to vote for your story – the 5 Finalists with the most votes will be eligible to win the Grand Prize of a trip home to Ontario’s great outdoors!</h3>
      <div class="your-adventure-button-bottom">
        <a href="/entries" class="button-main vote-canada-button-top">FIND YOUR FAVOURITE CANADIAN STORY</a>
      </div>
	  </div>
    </div>
  </div>
